      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "There must be something not quite right with this approach when trying to find my web session size: it reports 40, while ObjectGraphMeasurer (<a href=\"https://github.com/DimitrisAndreou/memory-measurer\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">github.com/DimitrisAndreou/memory-measurer</a>) reports &quot;Footprint{Objects=34, References=52, Primitives=[float, int x 19, char x 257, long x 2, byte x 68557]}&quot;. ObjectGraphMeasurer is clearly the winner."
